-- Megafon to Introduce LTE in 40 Cities This Year, Vedomosti Says
-- B y   K s e n i a   G a l o u c h k o
-- 2012-09-28T04:42:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-28/megafon-to-introduce-lte-in-40-cities-this-year-vedomosti-says.html
OAO Megafon, a Russian mobile
operator controlled by billionaire  Alisher Usmanov , plans to
introduce long-term evolution (LTE) connection technology in 40
cities by the end of the year,  Vedomosti  reported, citing a bond
prospectus.  To contact the reporter on this story:
